=== countdown_001 | countdown | Counts register n from 1 to 0 and emits several summaries
# family: countdown
# variant: 001
# initial register n: 1
# intended use: observe a very short halting witness
# small bound note: low budgets are enough here
# medium bound note: every reasonable run should halt
# large bound note: the verdict stays HALTS
# ranking hint: n decreases on every pass
# output note: ticks should equal the initial value
# checkpoint note: mirror tracks the current n
# branch note: loop_guard adds a tiny detour
# analyst question: how small can the bound be?
# expected shape: one loop and one halt path
set n 1
set ticks 0
set checksum 1
set mirror 1
set marker 1
bootstrap:
nop
nop
copy marker n
copy mirror n
loop:
jz n done
add ticks 1
sub n 1
copy mirror n
copy marker ticks
jnz mirror loop_guard
jump loop
loop_guard:
nop
jump loop
done:
out ticks
out checksum
out marker
halt
=== end

